          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protecting Americans from Gun Violence Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Centers for Disease Control to conduct or support gun violence research. It also requires a gun owner to report a lost or stolen firearm to local law enforcement authorities within 48 hours of discovery. </p>]]></text>
